HEADWORD: man of action
<hw>man of action</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who prefers to act
rather than contemplate and gets things accomplished quickly an
efficiently.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> man of deeds.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

